headline: HP (HPQ): Reassessing Valuation After Recent Share Price Volatility
summary: HP (HPQ) has had a choppy run lately, with the stock roughly flat over the past month but down about 10% in the past 3 months. This has raised questions about where value might be emerging. See our latest analysis for HP. Zooming out, HP’s share price has slipped meaningfully on a year to date basis despite a modest recent bounce.
